In a macabre discovery, three charred bodies of a 13-year-old and two adults, were found dead in a veld outside the Centurion estate, ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring said. Meiring said the paramedics arrived on the scene at around 8am.The initial assessment seemed to suggest that the bodies could have been bound before being set alight.&#8220;It would appear that the three patients were bound gagged and burned to death but this is subject to a postmortem and law enforcement investigation &#8221; he said.Meiring said on their arrival at the scene, all three victims of the dastardly act of violence were already dead as a result of their severe injuries, and that paramedics could nothing to help them. He added: We could do nothing to help them. TNA Reporter 